{
  "texts": [
    "We remark that neither K(σ) nor K[σ] are sub-p-adic for almost all σ ∈ G e K and any prime number p (see Proposition 5.1).",
    "Theorem 1.5.",
    "Let K be a finitely generated field over Q and e a positive integer.",
    "(1) (= Theorem 5.2) Any finite extension of K[σ] is Kummer-faithful for almost all σ ∈ G e K.",
    "(2) (= Theorem 5.3) The multiplicative group of K(σ) has no nontrivial divisible point for almost all σ ∈ G e K."
  ]
}